materasu||Gosha|| ||Kita, Ojihoncho|| |- |{{ill|Akasaka Hikawa Shrine|ja|赤坂氷川神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Akasaka Hikawa Shrine|qq=}}|| ||Susanoo, Kushinadahime, Okuninushi||Fusha|| ||Minato, Akasaka|| |}
