chifukujin|ja|深川七福神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Fukagawa Shichifukujin|qq=|1=Fukagawa Shichifukujin|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11559993}}.</ref><ref group="note">Left the Jinja Honcho in 2017.</ref> |- |{{ill|Oji Shrine (Kita-ku, Tokyo)|ja|王子神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Oji Shrine (Kita-ku, Tokyo)|qq=|1=Ōji Shrine (disambiguation)|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11573001}}||Oji Gongen||Izanagi, Izanami, Amaterasu||Gosha|| ||Kita, Ojihoncho|| |- |{{ill|Akasaka Hikawa Shrine|ja|赤坂氷川神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Akasaka Hikawa Shrine|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 氷川神社 (東京都港区赤坂)|1=Hikawa Shrine|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q3135503}}|| ||Susanoo, Kushinadahime, Okuninushi||Fusha|| ||Minato, Akasaka|| |}
